  "description": [
    "SIX Navy Unveils FY 63 Shipbuilding Program The Navy has unveiled an FY 1963 shipbuilding program that includes an attack aircraft carrier as well as 14 nuclear submarines and numerous amphibious patrol and auxiliary ships The new carrier will be a conventionallypowered ship of the Forrestal class It will replace a WWII Essex class carrier and will bring to nine the number of fully modern attack carriers Eight of these are of the Forrestal class while the ninth is the nuclear powered Enter prise NuclearPowe red Suits The Navy plans to build six fleet ballistic missile submarines each carrying 16 Polaris missiles as well as eight nuclearpowered subs designed primarily to de stroy enemy submarines This program will add eight to the 32 attack type submarines previously approved Guided Missile Frigate A nuclearpowered guided mis sile frigate featuring the new long and mediumranged Typhon surfacetoair surfacetosurface House Rejects Gl Insurance Program Plan The House has rejected a pro posal to reopen the GI insurance program to every veteran of WWII and the Korean conflict By a standing vote of 124 to 87 the House approved a meas ure limited to veterans disabled while in service This cut some 15 million"
